dlxs::buildTemplate()

Description
    private array dlxs::buildTemplate(string $file)
    Takes a template file as input and converts it into an array with each line of the file being an element in the array.

Parameters
    file
    	A file containing markup.

Return Values
    An array containing each line of the template.

Examples

Notes
	This function supports looping with the {dlxs repeat="start"} and {dlxs repeat="end"} tags. This can be useful if your data is repeated several times.
   
